story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0100: I see you’ve made it through the forest.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0300:
That far exceeds my expectations... But in the end,
mere Gym Leaders stand no chance against
Mewtwo now.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0400:
Well, that’s quite rude of you to say. Are you sure
you want to underestimate us?
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0500: I know the extent of your strength.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0600: You simply don’t have the power to stop Mewtwo.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0700: And just what do you mean by power, anyway?
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0800:
You mean the kind of power you get by hurting
Pokémon and using underlings like puppets?
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_0900: I don’t expect children like you to understand.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_1000: Though...I suppose some of you may, one day.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_1200: Perhaps that can be saved for another time.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_1300:
More importantly, I’m afraid I’ll have to ask you to
leave now.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_1400:
Get ready to feel a world of pain if you plan on
disobeying my orders.
story_teamrocket_01_23000/2401_1201_1500: You’re the one who should be worried right now!
